verbose_text: Quantum chemical calculations : The potential energy hypersurface was explored at the B97D/TZVP/TZVPfit level (in brief B97D) and refined at the MP2 / aug-cc-pVTZ level (MP2 / aug), including zero-point energy corrections (^ ZPE) at the same level and higher order correlation corrections at the ^ CCSD (T)/6-311+ G * level (CCSD (T)).
